Values.value: SELECT * FROM REQUEST_VERSIONS WHERE REQUEST_ID = '%requestId%' AND VERSION = '%version%' ORDER BY ID DESC;

SELECT DF.* FROM REQUEST_VERSIONS DF INNER JOIN (SELECT REQUEST_ID, MAX(VERSION) AS version FROM REQUEST_VERSIONS GROUP BY REQUEST_ID) D ON DF.REQUEST_ID = D.REQUEST_ID and DF.VERSION = D.version WHERE DF.REQUEST_ID='%requestId%' ORDER BY DF.ID DESC
